| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6700 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a7a9033f-146b-50b1-ade0-6675d5f69fb8"
